{"id":18106,"date":"2014-02-11T15:52:43","date_gmt":"2014-02-11T11:52:43","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/www.dailyhadithonline.com\/?p=18106"},"modified":"2019-08-02T21:45:39","modified_gmt":"2019-08-02T17:45:39","slug":"muhammad-maqam-mahmud","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/02\/11\/muhammad-maqam-mahmud\/","title":{"rendered":"Hadith on Paradise: The Prophet called to his praiseworthy station"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Hudhayfah reported: The people will be gathered upon the leveled earth and no soul will speak. The first to be called will be Muhammad, peace and blessings be upon him. The Prophet will say, \u201c<b>I am here at Your service. All good is in Your hand and evil cannot be ascribed to You. One will only be guided if You guide him. I am the servant, son of your servant, by You and for You. There is no escape or refuge from You but with You. Blessed and exalted are You.<\/b>\u201d This is the saying of Allah, \u201c<b>Perhaps He will raise you to a praiseworthy station.<\/b>\u201d (17:79)<\/p>\n<p>Source: al-Sunan al-Kubra\u0301 lil-Nasa\u0304\u2019i\u0304 10780<\/p>\n<p>Grade: <b><i>Sahih<\/i><\/b> (authentic) according to Ibn Hajar<\/p>\n<p align=\"right\">\u0639\u0646 \u062d\u0630\u064a\u0641\u0629 \u0642\u0627\u0644 \u064a\u064f\u062c\u0652\u0645\u064e\u0639\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0633\u064f \u0641\u0650\u064a \u0635\u064e\u0639\u0650\u064a\u062f\u064d \u0648\u064e\u0644\u0627 \u062a\u064e\u0643\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064f \u0646\u064e\u0641\u0652\u0633\u064c \u0641\u064e\u0623\u064e\u0648\u0651\u064e\u0644\u064f \u0645\u064e\u062f\u0652\u0639\u064f\u0648\u0651\u064d \u0645\u064f\u062d\u064e\u0645\u0651\u064e\u062f\u064c \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0641\u064e\u064a\u064e\u0642\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f<b>